    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 < 1.0 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating conditions, with validation evidence demonstrating adequate predictive fidelity for the intended comparative hemolysis decision. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
